@prefix ast: <https://repolex.ai/ontology/extracts/tree-sitter/tree-sitter/v0.25/core/> .
@prefix cmake: <https://repolex.ai/ontology/extracts/tree-sitter/tree-sitter/v0.25/lang/cmake/> .
